    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "mock.intercept actionPattern=\u0022http.request\u0022, returnValue={statusCode:200, headers:{}, body:{a:{b:42}}, duration:\u002200:00:00\u0022}, write to %m%",
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Mock http.request to return a Response-shaped value whose Body is a\ndeep dict. Asserts %resp.Body.a.b% reads through to 42, proving Data\nProperties navigation works on the typed Response result.\n(The actual Content-Type \u2192 Body parsing pipeline is covered end-to-end\nin C# by Stage3_HttpContentTypeDispatchTests.cs; this PLang test\nvalidates the user-visible navigation half.)",
